Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.30,0:01:22.49,EndOPED,,0,0,0,,out of countless others...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.49,0:01:26.08,Kar,,0,0,0,,{\k45}da{\k17}re {\k49}ni {\k25}mo {\k31}yu{\k36}zu{\k20}ri {\k22}ta{\k32}ku {\k45}wa {\k17}na{\k20}i
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.49,0:01:26.08,EndOPED,,0,0,0,,I feel that it should be to grab onto a dream
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.55,0:01:30.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰にも譲りたくはない\N夢を掴みたいと思うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.08,0:01:30.14,Kar,,0,0,0,,{\k40}yu{\k28}me {\k36}wo {\k46}tsu{\k30}ka{\k22}mi{\k23}ta{\k45}i {\k22}to {\k19}o{\k28}mo{\k37}u {\k29}yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.08,0:01:30.14,EndOPED,,0,0,0,,and never be tempted to let go.
