Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.98,0:22:46.05,EngED,,0,0,0,,Oh the ones being sung continuously
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.36,0:22:55.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,守られてまどろむ宵
